00:43:26.685 --> 00:43:29.948
I'm trying to find the
meaning of a symbol.


269
00:43:29.949 --> 00:43:31.342
Please, I'm desperate.

270
00:43:32.735 --> 00:43:34.518
One can plead with
the saints for mercy,


271
00:43:34.519 --> 00:43:37.260
but Morris, my
assistant, is no saint,


272
00:43:37.261 --> 00:43:38.827
or am I missing something?

273
00:43:38.828 --> 00:43:42.047
These people
were hoping to see you.


274
00:43:42.048 --> 00:43:45.224
I need to speak with you
just for a few minutes.


275
00:43:45.225 --> 00:43:47.271
Here at the door or inside?

276
00:44:15.995 --> 00:44:17.780
It's written in Latin.

277
00:44:19.303 --> 00:44:21.609
If you're here to ask my help,

278
00:44:21.610 --> 00:44:23.786
I imagine you believe
in the supernatural.


279
00:44:25.570 --> 00:44:28.485
Mrs. Nills, I saw the
symbol printed on this book


280
00:44:28.486 --> 00:44:30.619
carved on a box
that my niece found.


281
00:44:31.968 --> 00:44:33.404
May I ask where you found it?

282
00:44:34.797 --> 00:44:36.929
It was buried in the garden.

283
00:44:40.280 --> 00:44:41.672
If I were you,

284
00:44:41.673 --> 00:44:43.587
I would put it right
back where it was buried.


285
00:44:43.588 --> 00:44:45.328
It's a warning.

286
00:44:45.329 --> 00:44:47.765
This symbol means
it's possessed.


287
00:44:47.766 --> 00:44:48.811
I'll explain better.

288
00:44:50.465 --> 00:44:54.250
Sometimes, tormented souls
attach themselves to an object


289
00:44:54.251 --> 00:44:56.687
and are unable to let it go.

290
00:44:56.688 --> 00:44:59.168
Sort of like there
are haunted places,


291
00:44:59.169 --> 00:45:01.040
there are also haunted objects.

292
00:45:03.173 --> 00:45:04.913
The more time spent
with an object,


293
00:45:04.914 --> 00:45:06.305
the more its owner
connects with it,


294
00:45:06.306 --> 00:45:09.397
until they finally,
can't be without it.


295
00:45:10.702 --> 00:45:12.573
The tormented soul
can also affect


296
00:45:12.574 --> 00:45:14.401
the personality of the owner,

297
00:45:14.402 --> 00:45:16.794
making them absorb their
positive or negative energy,


298
00:45:16.795 --> 00:45:18.840
whatever the case may be.

299
00:45:18.841 --> 00:45:22.932
Well, positive or
negative in what sense?


300
00:45:24.281 --> 00:45:26.892
A possessed object
can be good luck


301
00:45:28.807 --> 00:45:31.462
if the spirit connected to
it experienced immense joy,


302
00:45:33.072 --> 00:45:34.856
while it can cause misery

303
00:45:34.857 --> 00:45:37.729
if the object was connected
with a tragic or sad event.


304
00:45:40.210 --> 00:45:43.343
So, if I understand
you correctly,


305
00:45:45.476 --> 00:45:47.129
the spirit makes a
strong connection


306
00:45:47.130 --> 00:45:50.001
with whoever comes to
possess the haunted object.


307
00:45:50.002 --> 00:45:51.002
Right?

308
00:45:52.178 --> 00:45:55.050
No, it's much worse.

309
00:45:55.051 --> 00:45:56.313
It conditions their life.

310
00:46:00.012 --> 00:46:01.231
Did you open the box?

311
00:46:04.539 --> 00:46:05.277
Yes.

312
00:46:05.278 --> 00:46:06.278
And, what was in it?

313
00:46:32.175 --> 00:46:34.569
Sophie, be careful!

314
00:46:36.135 --> 00:46:38.529
Don't wander around
the bookshelves.


315
00:46:58.070 --> 00:46:59.070
Sophie?

316
00:47:00.203 --> 00:47:01.203
Sophie?

317
00:49:42.017 --> 00:49:42.973
I'm sorry I'm late.

318
00:49:42.974 --> 00:49:45.933
That's okay, she's sleeping.

319
00:49:45.934 --> 00:49:48.022
I hope it wasn't too
much trouble for you


320
00:49:48.023 --> 00:49:49.589
No, not at all.

321
00:49:50.503 --> 00:49:52.941
Did you find Mrs. Nills?
Yes.


322
00:49:56.118 --> 00:49:57.118
Oh, sorry.

323
00:50:01.601 --> 00:50:02.601
Hello?

324
00:50:30.369 --> 00:50:33.589
Thank you so much
for everything,


325
00:50:33.590 --> 00:50:37.333
for being here with Sophie
and I, I really appreciate it.


326
00:50:58.963 --> 00:50:59.963
I'm sorry.

327
00:51:01.009 --> 00:51:02.009
It's not you.

328
00:51:04.360 --> 00:51:06.797
I'll call you tomorrow
to check on Sophie.


329
00:51:45.618 --> 00:51:46.663
Is somebody there?

330
00:51:52.277 --> 00:51:53.670
Dumb mice.

331
00:52:51.815 --> 00:52:54.687
No!

332
00:53:02.043 --> 00:53:03.043
Sophie.

333
00:53:05.263 --> 00:53:06.612
Sophie, calm down!

334
00:53:09.746 --> 00:53:12.095
Don't ever do that
again, do you understand?


335
00:53:12.096 --> 00:53:13.618
You're not my mother!

336
00:53:20.061 --> 00:53:21.061
Sophie!

337
00:53:46.087 --> 00:53:47.914
Hi, have you seen a little girl?

338
00:53:47.915 --> 00:53:49.219
She's over there.

339
00:53:49.220 --> 00:53:50.307
Okay.

340
00:53:50.308 --> 00:53:52.962
Okay.

341
00:53:52.963 --> 00:53:54.268
Is Eva off today?

342
00:53:54.269 --> 00:53:55.486
She's in the hospital.

343
00:53:55.487 --> 00:53:56.793
We found her unconscious.

344
00:53:59.274 --> 00:54:00.623
Oh my God, that's awful.

345
00:54:11.199 --> 00:54:12.591
Everything all right at school?

346
00:54:23.733 --> 00:54:25.690
Sophie, can I see your carillon?

347
00:54:25.691 --> 00:54:26.779
No.

348
00:54:30.870 --> 00:54:32.175
What if I just
take it for tonight,


349
00:54:32.176 --> 00:54:34.047
and I give it back tomorrow?

350
00:54:34.048 --> 00:54:35.048
No.

351
00:54:38.269 --> 00:54:40.140
Sophie, give me the carillon.

352
00:54:41.359 --> 00:54:46.538
Sophie!

353
00:55:07.472 --> 00:55:09.735
Sophie, don't worry, sweetie.

354
00:55:12.303 --> 00:55:13.303
It's okay.

355
00:55:16.742 --> 00:55:17.961
Lania is mean.

356
00:55:20.094 --> 00:55:22.096
She can't be mean if
we bury the carillon.


357
00:55:28.015 --> 00:55:30.842
Don't go away, you too.

358
00:55:30.843 --> 00:55:32.496
What are you talking about?

359
00:55:32.497 --> 00:55:34.542
I'll never go away,

360
00:55:34.543 --> 00:55:37.589
but honey, we have
to bury the carillon.


361
00:55:38.808 --> 00:55:40.114
Okay, tomorrow?

362
00:55:43.943 --> 00:55:44.943
Tomorrow.

363
00:57:48.938 --> 00:57:51.026
Did you bury it?

364
00:57:51.027 --> 00:57:53.638
Yes, sweetheart
the carillon is gone.


365
00:59:51.408 --> 00:59:54.062
I buried the box
but it didn't work,


366
00:59:54.063 --> 00:59:55.282
Then all this happened.

367
01:00:15.214 --> 01:00:17.520
So, you say it's the
spirit of a little girl?


368
01:00:17.521 --> 01:00:19.610
Yes, Lania, that's her name.

369
01:00:21.308 --> 01:00:23.744
At least that's what
Sophie calls her.


370
01:00:23.745 --> 01:00:26.964
And, your niece sees her
all the time and talks to her?


371
01:00:26.965 --> 01:00:31.186
Yes, she dug up
the box by herself,


372
01:00:31.187 --> 01:00:32.188
maybe that's why.

373
01:00:33.842 --> 01:00:34.843
May I see the box?

374
01:00:46.898 --> 01:00:48.813
Do you know who lived
here before you?


375
01:00:50.424 --> 01:00:53.992
Yes, of course Mrs. White,
but I didn't know her.


376
01:00:55.603 --> 01:00:57.605
So, you don't know what
she did in this house?


377
01:01:02.218 --> 01:01:03.524
She was a psychic herself.

378
01:01:04.786 --> 01:01:05.874
In those days,

379
01:01:07.745 --> 01:01:09.356
I mean when I was just a girl,

380
01:01:10.705 --> 01:01:12.881
people believed much
more in these things.


381
01:01:14.186 --> 01:01:16.927
They would come from
town to ask for her help.


382
01:01:16.928 --> 01:01:18.408
She had this kind of gift.

383
01:01:20.105 --> 01:01:21.977
She could speak to spirits.

384
01:01:25.894 --> 01:01:27.374
This is the symbol.

385
01:01:29.201 --> 01:01:30.680
The carillon is inside,

386
01:01:30.681 --> 01:01:31.987
correct?
Yes.


387
01:01:37.862 --> 01:01:39.124
It was locked inside here.

388
01:01:40.996 --> 01:01:42.824
This is certainly
not a good spirit.


389
01:02:22.516 --> 01:02:23.516
Morris?

390
01:02:43.493 --> 01:02:44.538
May I?

391
01:02:45.756 --> 01:02:46.756
Yes.

392
01:03:04.383 --> 01:03:07.081
Mrs. White knew the
world of the afterlife


393
01:03:07.082 --> 01:03:08.387
very intimately.

394
01:03:10.172 --> 01:03:12.740
She knew how to defend
herself from evil.


395
01:03:14.568 --> 01:03:16.091
This is a protective symbol.

396
01:03:18.528 --> 01:03:22.227
The spirit of this child has
been, let's say, weakened,


397
01:03:23.838 --> 01:03:26.317
because this house is protected.

398
01:03:26.318 --> 01:03:28.972
This is the safest
room in the house.


399
01:03:28.973 --> 01:03:30.497
Mrs. White probably worked here,

400
01:03:32.368 --> 01:03:35.718
however this protection
won't last forever.


401
01:03:35.719 --> 01:03:37.807
Generally, in cases
such as these,


402
01:03:37.808 --> 01:03:39.114
the more time passes,

403
01:03:40.507 --> 01:03:42.333
the more the person
that has the object


404
01:03:42.334 --> 01:03:45.467
becomes attached to
that possessed object.


405
01:03:45.468 --> 01:03:47.208
Simply put,

406
01:03:47.209 --> 01:03:50.385
the more time your niece
spends with the carillon,


407
01:03:50.386 --> 01:03:52.430
the more powerful
the spirit becomes,


408
01:03:52.431 --> 01:03:54.781
regardless of where it is,

409
01:03:54.782 --> 01:03:57.393
because, in a certain
sense, they become one.


410
01:04:00.178 --> 01:04:03.007
We, we did didn't do anything
when we buried it again.


411
01:04:05.227 --> 01:04:07.054
What do we do?

412
01:04:07.055 --> 01:04:08.404
I'm sorry, I don't know.

413
01:04:14.671 --> 01:04:17.238
Let's ask Mrs. 
White for help.

414
01:04:17.239 --> 01:04:18.239
Morris?

415
01:04:42.177 --> 01:04:45.789
Mrs. White, you
lived in this house.


416
01:04:48.096 --> 01:04:49.532
I need to speak with you.

417
01:04:51.969 --> 01:04:55.843
If your spirit is with
us, please give me a sign.


418
01:05:04.068 --> 01:05:08.637
Mrs. White, if your
spirit is with us,


419
01:05:08.638 --> 01:05:10.205
please, give me a sign.

420
01:05:27.396 --> 01:05:30.398
Hopefully, we can try
again another day.


421
01:05:30.399 --> 01:05:32.531
Alright, thanks.

422
01:05:33.924 --> 01:05:37.361
Put everything back
exactly as it was.


423
01:05:37.362 --> 01:05:38.841
It's a child spirit.

424
01:05:38.842 --> 01:05:41.018
It must know that
you are in control.


425
01:07:35.176 --> 01:07:36.176
Third step.

426
01:08:19.524 --> 01:08:23.790
September 10,

427
01:08:25.835 --> 01:08:27.923
Mrs. Roseline Potter
asked for my help.


428
01:08:27.924 --> 01:08:31.100
A case of a possessed object,

429
01:08:31.101 --> 01:08:33.887
a carillon linked to the
spirit of a child named Lania.


430
01:08:35.497 --> 01:08:37.454
I shut the carillon in
a box and buried it,


431
01:08:37.455 --> 01:08:39.761
so that the spirit
connected to the object


432
01:08:39.762 --> 01:08:41.372
may rest in peace.

433
01:09:01.784 --> 01:09:02.784
Hello?

434
01:09:11.925 --> 01:09:14.274
She felt really sick
during the session.


435
01:09:14.275 --> 01:09:17.581
I figured it was better not to
wait, so I brought her here.


436
01:09:17.582 --> 01:09:18.887
How is she now?

