01:09:18.888 --> 01:09:20.672
The doctor is
inside with her now.


438
01:09:36.950 --> 01:09:39.343
How is she?
Are you her parents?


439
01:09:40.562 --> 01:09:42.824
No, I'm her aunt.

440
01:09:42.825 --> 01:09:44.782
She has got a really high fever.

441
01:09:44.783 --> 01:09:46.175
We're doing more tests

442
01:09:46.176 --> 01:09:48.438
to try and understand
what the matter is.


443
01:09:48.439 --> 01:09:51.094
Medication doesn't seem to
have had an effect so far.


444
01:10:12.202 --> 01:10:14.551
The carillon.
No, sweetie.


445
01:10:14.552 --> 01:10:15.552
The carillon.

446
01:10:19.731 --> 01:10:21.820
I want to hear it, please.

447
01:10:46.193 --> 01:10:49.760
The doctor says that her
condition is back to normal.


448
01:10:49.761 --> 01:10:51.459
Tests show everything is fine.

449
01:10:53.156 --> 01:10:54.940
They'll keep an
eye on her tonight


450
01:10:54.941 --> 01:10:56.551
and release her
tomorrow morning.


