01:11:07.910 --> 01:11:09.955
The doctor says she's fine.

454
01:11:09.956 --> 01:11:10.956
Don't worry.

455
01:11:13.568 --> 01:11:16.048
I saw that Sophie is
starting to speak again.


456
01:11:16.049 --> 01:11:18.050
Yeah, and the first
thing she said to me


