01:12:12.888 --> 01:12:13.714
What do you want to eat?

464
01:12:13.715 --> 01:12:14.716
Should we order a pizza?

465
01:13:30.792 --> 01:13:32.793
Okay, yeah.

466
01:13:32.794 --> 01:13:34.795
I just need you
for another hour.


467
01:13:34.796 --> 01:13:35.883
In the diary of Mrs. White,

468
01:13:35.884 --> 01:13:37.145
I found the person who asked her

469
01:13:37.146 --> 01:13:38.973
for help with the carillon.

470
01:13:38.974 --> 01:13:40.931
I wanna go talk to her.

471
01:13:40.932 --> 01:13:42.803
Sure, don't worry.

472
01:13:42.804 --> 01:13:44.327
Okay, thank you.

473
01:14:04.347 --> 01:14:06.261
Are you Mrs. Roseline Potter?

474
01:14:06.262 --> 01:14:08.481
Yes, who wants to know?

475
01:14:08.482 --> 01:14:10.874
Hello, I'm sorry,
you don't know me.


476
01:14:10.875 --> 01:14:13.181
My name is Annabelle Spear.

477
01:14:13.182 --> 01:14:14.704
I need your help.

478
01:14:14.705 --> 01:14:16.576
What's this about?

479
01:14:16.577 --> 01:14:19.492
I know that, years
ago, you had a carillon.


480
01:14:19.493 --> 01:14:20.754
Go away!

481
01:14:20.755 --> 01:14:22.756
No, no Mrs. Potter,
please, please!


482
01:14:22.757 --> 01:14:24.236
I need to talk to you.

483
01:14:24.237 --> 01:14:26.238
I know about your daughter Jade.

484
01:14:26.239 --> 01:14:29.502
Please, it's about my
niece, she's only six.


485
01:14:29.503 --> 01:14:30.503
Please.

486
01:14:33.376 --> 01:14:34.421
Come on.

487
01:14:39.774 --> 01:14:41.210
I didn't think to
contact a psychic


488
01:14:42.951 --> 01:14:45.388
until after the death
of my daughter, Jade.


489
01:14:46.781 --> 01:14:47.869
Mrs. White.

490
01:14:50.437 --> 01:14:54.397
Lania, after Jade was gone,

491
01:14:55.529 --> 01:14:57.226
manifested herself to me.

492
01:14:58.923 --> 01:15:00.620
She didn't try to hurt me.

493
01:15:00.621 --> 01:15:03.188
She was just there, next to me.

494
01:15:03.189 --> 01:15:05.321
She was there always,

495
01:15:07.105 --> 01:15:09.325
until Mrs. White found
a way to free me.


496
01:15:11.458 --> 01:15:14.417
She put the carillon in
a box and she buried it.


497
01:15:19.292 --> 01:15:21.381
My niece found it
playing in the garden


498
01:15:24.035 --> 01:15:25.472
and since then, it's,

499
01:15:26.864 --> 01:15:28.257
it's been a nightmare.

500
01:15:29.780 --> 01:15:31.912
Do you know exactly
what Mrs. White did?


501
01:15:31.913 --> 01:15:34.436
I tried burying the box again.

502
01:15:34.437 --> 01:15:36.656
It didn't make any difference.

503
01:15:36.657 --> 01:15:38.702
I'm sorry, I don't know.

504
01:15:46.623 --> 01:15:50.191
Where did she get the carillon?

505
01:15:50.192 --> 01:15:52.412
She got it at an antiques fair.

506
01:15:54.109 --> 01:15:56.589
My daughter couldn't
be separated from it.


507
01:15:56.590 --> 01:15:58.809
She listened to it all the time.

508
01:16:01.377 --> 01:16:02.769
In the beginning,

509
01:16:02.770 --> 01:16:05.075
she said she was playing
with a little girl.


510
01:16:05.076 --> 01:16:07.339
I didn't believe her.

511
01:16:07.340 --> 01:16:09.342
I just thought she
wanted more attention.


512
01:16:11.909 --> 01:16:13.433
Then she started to get sick.

513
01:16:15.130 --> 01:16:17.697
She had this high
incurable fever.


514
01:16:17.698 --> 01:16:19.176
It would come and go.

515
01:16:19.177 --> 01:16:21.310
She'd seem to get better
and then she'd get worse.


516
01:16:24.966 --> 01:16:26.272
I'll never forget that night.

517
01:16:29.275 --> 01:16:32.842
I was, I was sitting
there reading


518
01:16:32.843 --> 01:16:37.456
and when I heard the carillon
