whole thing through.


520
01:16:39.023 --> 01:16:40.460
It would always get stuck.

521
01:16:43.593 --> 01:16:45.681
I just felt something was wrong.

522
01:16:45.682 --> 01:16:48.903
I went to try and find Jade.

523
01:16:51.775 --> 01:16:53.168
I found her there on the sofa.

524
01:16:55.039 --> 01:16:56.779
She was dead.

525
01:16:56.780 --> 01:16:58.173
She'd been smothered.

526
01:17:00.871 --> 01:17:03.265
The carillon was
there next to her.


527
01:17:06.660 --> 01:17:08.749
If only I'd believed her.

528
01:17:13.101 --> 01:17:17.322
Do you wake up with rose
